snippet.title: Zombie Night Terror Trailer
snippet.description:
Zombie Night Terror is a lemmings-like game teeming with hordes of zombies craving for fresh meat.

Website: http://www.zombienightterror.com
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/zombienightterror
Twitter: https://twitter.com/ZN_Terror

Music by Christophe Blondel : https://twitter.com/CarboHydroM
